                  He was also the counsellor and intimate friend of King <persName ref="PRS9038Susenyos">Susǝnyos</persName>
                  
               </floruit>
               <death when="1638">He died in <date>1638</date> probably at <placeName ref="LOC3098Fogara"/> where he lived for some years after he was dismissed  
